metadata.name: Siren Sword by Ghost Train
metadata.description:
Siren Sword is an original 3D art piece by Ghost Train
commemorating the completion of the Nemesis collection.

This NFT provides access to Ghost Train's upcoming collector community and Allowlist access to premint prices.

Free mint is only available from 6:30 pm - Midnight Fri Mar 31

About Nemesis Collection:
Nemesis is a story about duality;
A duet of light and darkness told in two audiovisual character drops;
The Last Paladin (sold out) and The First Knight (available now)

Both pieces feature original 3D Animated Art and Music by Ghost Train,
And come with derivative rights and a 3rd additional piece airdropped to collectors of both pieces.

Nemesis Collection:
opensea.io/collection/nemesis-art-music-nft

Ghost Train is a 3D art and Music NFT Duo from Toronto, Canada
Art: Tim Byrne
Music: Matt Sims
